on the page: https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/BITBUCKET/Convert+from+Subversion+to+Mercurial

In the section after you&#x27;ve run

{code}
#!bash

hg convert,
{code}

then change to the converted directory, you need to run (last code block, between pwd and hg push)

{code}
#!bash

hg update
{code}

The lack of hg update is the bug.  See Mercurial docs, http://mercurial.selenic.com/wiki/ConvertExtension  which match my experience.  I am calling this a blocker because without it, the procedure will not succeed.

before you can

{code}
#!bash

 hg push
{code}

